ce:section.ce:para:
Bovine serum albumin (BSA), lactoferrin (LF), ovalbumin (OVA), complete and incomplete Freund’s adjuvant, HAT Supplement, HT Supplement, PEG 1500, human immunoglobulin G (IgG), acetylcholinesterase (AChE), glucose oxidase (GOD), peroxidase from horseradish (HRP) and trypsin were all supplied by Sigma-Aldrich Co., Ltd. (St. Louis, MO, USA). Penicillin-Streptomycin, RPMI Medium 1640 basic(1X) and GlutaMAX were offered by Thermo Fisher Scientific (Waltham, MA, USA). Fetal calf serum was supplied by ExCell Bio. Co., Ltd. (Shanghai, China). Cell saving was provided by New Cell & Molecular Biotech Co., Ltd. (Suzhou, China). (3-aminopropyl)trimethoxysilane, Ascorbic acid (AA) and 2-phospho-l-ascorbic acid trisodium salt (AAP) were supplied by Aladdin Industrial Corporation (Shanghai, China). NaNO2, (NH4)2SO4, Na2CO3, NaHCO3, Na3PO4, Na2HPO4 and octanoic acid were brought from Tianjin Chemical Reagent Co., Ltd. (Tianjin, China). Dopamine, C18, Primary secondary amine, ethyl-3-aminobenzoate, 4-aminobenzoic acid, diammonium citrate, sodium chloride, magnesium sulfate and urea were supplied by Yien Chemical Technology Co., Ltd. (Shanghai, China). The AttoPhos AP fluorescent substrate system was purchased from Promega (Madison, WI). Standard solutions of benzocaine (BZC), procaine, tricaine, eugenol, quinaldine, lidocaine and propofol were supplied by Tan-Mo Technology Co., Ltd. (Beijing, China). Anti-BZC monoclonal antibody (mAb) was produced by our laboratory (the production procedure was detailed in the 
                           Supplementary Materials
                        ).
